        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/beanbean66/" class="name">迷你型啤酒桶</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2008-08-11" class="main-meta">2008-08-11 10:22:46</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2136133/">北京十月文艺出版社2007版</a>
            </span>
